          style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>papillary fibroelastomas</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>脂肪瘤（</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>lipomas</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>橫紋肌瘤</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>
          </span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'
          lang=3Dzh-TW>（</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'
          lang=3Dzh-TW>rhabdomyomas</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
          font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>）</span></li>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>纖維瘤（</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>fibromas</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>血管瘤（</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>hemangiomas</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>畸胎瘤（</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>teratomas</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>淋巴管瘤（</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>lymphangiomas</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
     </ul>
    </ul>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>惡性</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>：較常見發生在</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
        font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'>右心房</span></li>
    <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
     margin-bottom:0in'>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
         style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
         11.0pt'>肉瘤</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
         font-size:11.0pt'>：</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
         font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>大部分</span></li>
     <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
      margin-bottom:0in'>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>血管肉瘤（</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>angiosarcoma</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）、橫紋肌肉瘤（</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>rhabdomyosarcoma</span><span
