       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>10% </span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>患者無症狀</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>大多數患者會出現</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'
       lang=3Dzh-TW>典型</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;
       font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US> Triad</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>血流阻塞（</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
        font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>O</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'
        lang=3Dzh-TW>bstruction of blood flow</span><span style=3D'font-weight:
        bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>）</span></li>
    <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
     margin-bottom:0in'>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
         style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
         11.0pt'>左心房腫瘤</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
         font-size:11.0pt'>：症狀</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:
         "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'>可類似二尖瓣病變</span></li>
     <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
      margin-bottom:0in'>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>呼吸困難、肺水腫</span></li>
      <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
       margin-bottom:0in'>
       <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
           style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Dyspnea on exertion</span></li>
       <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
           style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>陣發性夜間呼吸困難（</span><span
           style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>paroxysmal nocturnal
           dyspnea</span></li>
       <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
           style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>仰臥呼吸困難（</span><span
           style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>orthopnea</span><span
           style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
      </ul>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>心悸</span></li>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>暫時性瓣膜出口阻塞（</span><span
          style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>transient valve orifice
          occlusion</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
          font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
      <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
       margin-bottom:0in'>
       <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
           style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'
           lang=3Den-US>若出現會造成</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
           font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>較嚴重的表現：</span><span style=3D'font-weight:
           bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'
           lang=3Dzh-TW>暈厥、低血壓、猝死</span></li>
      </ul>
     </ul>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
         style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
         11.0pt'>右心房腫瘤</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
         font-size:11.0pt'>：症狀</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:
         "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'>類似右心衰竭</span></li>
     <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
      margin-bottom:0in'>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#ED7D31'><span
          style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
          11.0pt'>肝腫大、腹水、周邊水腫</span></li>
     </ul>
     <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
      margin-bottom:0in'>
      <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
          style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>心室出口阻塞較左心房罕見，但若腫瘤太大也可能導致</span></li>
     </ul>
    </ul>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>腫瘤栓塞（</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
        font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>T</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'
        lang=3Dzh-TW>umor embolization</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
        font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>）</span></li>
    <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
     margin-bottom:0in'>
